OL,3,CChristmas lights trail being
OL,4,Cvandalised 'on a daily basis'
OL,6,FA Christmas lights trail in Devon is
OL,7,Fbeing vandalised "on a daily basis"
OL,8,Fand contractors repairing and checking
OL,9,Fthe damage have also faced abuse,
OL,10,Faccording to Torbay Council.
OL,12,FThe damaged lights are part of the Bay
OL,13,Fof Lights Illumination Trail which has
OL,14,Fbeen coordinated by the council.
OL,16,FThe council says it is working with
OL,17,Fagencies, including Devon and Cornwall
OL,18,FPolice, to identify and deal with the
OL,19,Findividuals that are responsible for
OL,20,Fthe damage.
