OL,3,CChristmas lights trail being
OL,4,Cvandalised 'on a daily basis'
OL,6,FThe council said: "We will be putting
OL,7,Fin place extra measures over the
OL,8,Fcoming days to proactively deal with
OL,9,Fthis unacceptable behaviour. If you
OL,10,Fspot anyone causing damage, please
OL,11,Freport it to the police.
OL,13,F"We would also like to remind people
OL,14,Fthat all the light installations are
OL,15,Fthere to be visually enjoyed and
OL,16,Fshould not be touched or played with."
OL,18,FThe Bay of Lights includes a 1.5-mile
OL,19,FIllumination Trail in Torquay which is
OL,20,Fnow in its third year.
