OL,3,CChristmas lights trail being
OL,4,Cvandalised 'on a daily basis'
OL,6,FIt's a free event and lights up
OL,7,FTorquay's seafront, Torre Abbey and
OL,8,Fthe harbourside every evening until
OL,9,FThursday 2 January. The light
OL,10,Finstallations will run daily from
OL,11,F4.30pm, with sound elements until
OL,12,F9.30pm and lighting until 11pm.
OL,14,FEighteen large installations are part
OL,15,Fof the trail with a new LED light
OL,16,Ffountain, 1,000 colour changing hand
OL,17,Fplaced flowers, pixel pads and a giant
OL,18,Fwalk-through Christmas present.
